Description: Admin user should be able to log in using valid credentials
User should be able to click the Clients option from the left navigation panel
User should be able to put characters on Search bar
User should be able to search clients
User should be able to Click Advance search button
User should be able to search clients using Client name
User should be able to select Status Dropdown button
User should be able to put characters on Address field
User should be able to search or select Country on Tyoe-in search dropdown
User should be able to search or select State on Tyoe-in search dropdown

User should be able to search clients using Contact name
User should be able to search clients using Contact Email
